data.description: Splendid in every way! Brilliant sun throughout by way of the abundant windows. Wonderfully designed with soaring vaulted ceilings. Delightfully open concept with ample great room and dining. Step out to the newer deck overlooking a fabulous yard with firepit and nature. Wonderful kitchen with center island slate backsplash and plentiful cabinetry, stainless appliances, six-panel doors, large front foyer, ceramic tile in baths, separate owner’s bath, and private lower-level guest room. The large, finished laundry room has an abundance of storage. Charming, new carriage-style garage doors and insulated and heated garage with workbench. Beautifully finished walkout lower level with pool table, wet bar, game table space, recreation, and movie entertainment areas with a cozy gas fireplace and more. Perfect for multi-generational living. Step out to the paver patio. Lovingly cared for in a quiet high-demand neighborhood.  Conveniently located near shopping, entertainment, and I-94 access.
